embeds.title: Self Roles
embeds.description:
:white_check_mark: for : `I'm finished with self roles` (MUST HAVE AT LEAST ONE)
:bell: for: `Announcement Pings` (We will ping you for announcements and you will be able to see those channels)
:handshake: for: `Partner Ping` (When a partnered server or member sends there server they can ping this role and notify all people with this role)

fields.name: What to do when finished?
fields.value: Please go to the rules chat and follow directions there
